Lesson 3 
1.	Applied Steps oynasining maqsadi nima?
o	O‘zbekcha: Applied Steps oynasi sizning barcha o‘zgarishlaringizni ketma-ket ko‘rsatadi. Siz qadamlarni tahrirlash, o‘chirish yoki tartibini o‘zgartirish imkoniga egasiz.
o	Inglizcha: The Applied Steps pane shows all the transformations you applied in order. You can edit, delete, or reorder steps.
2.	Takroriy qatorlarni qanday olib tashlash mumkin?
o	O‘zbekcha: Jadvalni tanlang → Home → Remove Rows → Remove Duplicates. Takroriy qatorlarning birinchisi qoladi, qolganlari o‘chiriladi.
o	Inglizcha: Select the table → Home → Remove Rows → Remove Duplicates. The first occurrence of duplicates remains, the rest are removed.
3.	Filter ikonkasi nima qiladi?
o	O‘zbekcha: Filter ikonkasi satrlarni tanlash yoki filtrlash imkonini beradi. Masalan, ma’lum qiymatlarni tanlash, shartlar qo‘yish, matnni qidirish.
o	Inglizcha: The Filter icon allows you to select or filter rows, for example by specific values, conditions, or text search.
4.	CustID ustunini CustomerID deb qanday o‘zgartirish mumkin?
o	O‘zbekcha: Ustunga o‘ng tugma → Rename → yangi nomni yozing. Yoki ustunni ikki marta bosib tahrirlash mumkin.
o	Inglizcha: Right-click the column → Rename → type the new name. Or double-click the column header to edit.
5.	Close & Apply bosilsa nima bo‘ladi?
o	O‘zbekcha: Barcha o‘zgarishlar saqlanadi va Power BI Desktop ga yuklanadi.
o	Inglizcha: All changes are saved and loaded back into Power BI Desktop.
6.	Quantity < 2 bo‘lgan qatorlarni olib tashlash
o	O‘zbekcha: Quantity ustunini filtrlash: Number Filters → Greater than or equal to 2.
o	Inglizcha: Filter the Quantity column → Number Filters → Greater than or equal to 2.
7.	OrderDate ustunini Year, Month, Day ga ajratish
o	O‘zbekcha: OrderDate ustunini tanlang → Transform → Date → Year/Month/Day → Extract yoki Split Column.
o	Inglizcha: Select OrderDate → Transform → Date → Year/Month/Day → Extract or use Split Column.
8.	Product ustunidagi “Mouse” ni “Computer Mouse” bilan almashtirish
o	O‘zbekcha: Product ustuni → Transform → Replace Values → “Mouse” ni “Computer Mouse” bilan almashtiring.
o	Inglizcha: Product column → Transform → Replace Values → replace “Mouse” with “Computer Mouse”.
9.	Jadvalni OrderDate bo‘yicha (eng yangi birinchi) tartiblash
o	O‘zbekcha: OrderDate ustunini tanlang → Sort Descending.
o	Inglizcha: Select OrderDate → Sort Descending.
10.	Price ustunidagi null qiymatlarni qanday boshqarish mumkin?
o	O‘zbekcha: Null qiymatlarni 0 bilan almashtirish, qatorlarni o‘chirish yoki Fill Down/Up yordamida to‘ldirish mumkin.
o	Inglizcha: Replace nulls with 0, remove rows, or use Fill Down/Up to fill missing values.
11.	TotalSpent = Quantity * Price ustunini qo‘shish
o	O‘zbekcha: Add Column → Custom Column → TotalSpent = [Quantity] * [Price].
o	Inglizcha: Add Column → Custom Column → TotalSpent = [Quantity] * [Price].
12.	CustID bo‘yicha guruhlab jami xarajatni ko‘rsatish
o	O‘zbekcha: Home → Group By → CustID → Sum → TotalSpent.
o	Inglizcha: Home → Group By → CustID → Sum → TotalSpent.
13.	Turli sana formatlarini tuzatish
o	O‘zbekcha: OrderDate ustunini tanlang → Transform → Data Type → Date. Power Query turli formatlarni bir xil formatga o‘tkazadi.
o	Inglizcha: Select OrderDate → Transform → Data Type → Date. Power Query converts different date formats to a consistent format.
14.	Shartli ustun: Price > 100 bo‘lsa “High Value” deb belgilash
o	O‘zbekcha: Add Column → Conditional Column → nomi OrderLabel, shart: Price > 100 → “High Value”, aks holda “Normal”.
o	Inglizcha: Add Column → Conditional Column → name OrderLabel, condition: Price > 100 → “High Value”, else “Normal”.
15.	So‘rovni optimallashtirish
o	O‘zbekcha: Keraksiz ustunlarni oldinroq olib tashlash, satrlarni filtrlash, ortiqcha qadamlarni kamaytirish.
o	Inglizcha: Remove unnecessary columns early, filter rows, and reduce extra steps to optimize query.

